0150325061911/http://www.theverge.com/2015/3/24/8284781/internet-explorer-is-slowly-dying |archivedate=2015-03-25 }}</ref><ref name="ieblog-edge">{{cite web |title=Living on the Edge – our next step in helping the web just work |url=http://blogs.msdn.com/b/ie/archive/2014/11/11/living-on-the-edge-our-next-step-in-interoperability.aspx |website=IEBlog |publisher=Microsoft |accessdate=2015-01-23 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150111145128/http://blogs.msdn.com/b/ie/archive/2014/11/11/living-on-the-edge-our-next-step-in-interoperability.aspx |archivedate=2015-01-11 }}</ref>

Windows 10整合Microsoft的[[智能个人助理|智能个人助理]]——[[Cortana|Cortana]]，微軟在2014年首次引入其至Windows Phone 8.1。Cortana取代Windows的嵌入式搜索功能，支援文本和语音输入。它的许多功能是从Windows Phone直接移植的，包括与[[Bing|Bing]]的整合、设置提醒、用于管理个人信息的「笔记本」功能，其可用以搜索文件、播放音乐、启动应用程序和设置提醒，还有发送电子邮件。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.zdnet.com/article/windows-10-can-cortana-persuade-us-to-talk-to-our-tech/ |title=Windows 10: Can Cortana persuade us to talk to our tech? |last1=Kingsley-Hughes |first1=Adrian |date=2015-01-21 |website=ZDNet |publisher=CBS Interactive |access-date=2015-03-17 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150322054718/http://www.zdnet.com/article/windows-10-can-cortana-persuade-us-to-talk-to-our-tech/ |archivedate=2015-03-22 }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://arstechnica.com/information-technology/2015/01/windows-10-brings-cortana-to-the-desktop/ |title=Windows 10 brings Cortana to the desktop |last1=Gallagher |first1=Sean |date=2015-01-22 |website=Ars Technica |publisher=Condé Nast |access-date=2015-03-17 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150311164418/http://arstechnica.com/information-technology/2015/01/windows-10-brings-cortana-to-the-desktop/ |archivedate=2015-03-11 }}</ref>

[[微軟家長監護服務|微軟家長監護服務]]則由Microsoft家庭取代，其是一套適用於Windows平台和Microsoft在線服務的父母監控系統。用户可在「您的家庭」中创建指定的家庭及新增家庭成員，并监控和限制指定为儿童用户的操作，例如访问网站，在Windows应用商店购买应用时实施年龄评级以及其他限制。该服务还可向家长发送每周电子邮件报告，详细说明儿童的计算机使用情况。与以前版本的Windows不同，家庭中的子帐户必须与Microsoft帐户相关联，允许这些设置适用于特定孩子使用的Windows 10设备。<ref name="thurrott-family">{{cite web|title=Inside Microsoft Family and Windows 10 Parental Controls|url=https://www.thurrott.com/windows/windows-10/5187/inside-microsoft-family-and-windows-10-parental-controls|website=Thurrott.com|accessdate=2015-09-12|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150925153702/https://www.thurrott.com/windows/windows-10/5187/inside-microsoft-family-and-windows-10-parental-controls|archivedate=2015-09-25}}</ref><ref name="bi-emailfamily">{{cite web|title=People are freaking out over a feature in Windows 10's family accounts|url=http://uk.businessinsider.com/there-are-privacy-concerns-over-windows-10s-family-activity-report-2015-8|first=Max|last=Slater-Robins|date=2015-08-27|accessdate=2015-09-12|work=[[Business_Insider|Business Insider]]|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150831011934/http://uk.businessinsider.com/there-are-privacy-concerns-over-windows-10s-family-activity-report-2015-8|archivedate=2015-08-31}}</ref>

Windows 10还提供源自Windows Phone 8.1的Wi-Fi Sense功能；用户可以选择让他们的设备自动连接到建议的开放热点，并与联系人共享其家庭网络的密码（通过[[Skype|Skype]]，[[Outlook.com|連絡人]]或[[Facebook|Facebook]]），他们可以自动连接到Windows 10设备上，而无需手动输入密码。密码則以加密形式存储在Microsoft服务器上，并发送到所选联系人的设备。访客用户不能查看密码，也不允许访问网络上的其他计算机或设备。 Wi-Fi Sense不能在[[802.1X|802.1X]]加密网络上使用。在[[SSID|SSID]]末尾添加「_optout」也会阻止相应的网络被應用于此功能。<ref name="pcworld-wifisense">{{cite web|title=Windows 10's Wi-Fi Sense password sharing sparks security concerns|url=http://www.pcworld.com/article/2943752/wifi-passwordsharing-feature-in-windows-10-raises-security-concerns.html|website=[[PC_World|PC World]]|publisher=[[IDG|IDG]]|accessdate=2015-07-18|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150721203813/http://www.pcworld.com/article/2943752/wifi-passwordsharing-feature-in-windows-10-raises-security-concerns.html|archivedate=2015-07-21}}</ref>

=== 多媒體和遊戲 ===
Windows 10与[[Xbox|Xbox]]生态系统的更加紧密。 Xbox SmartGlass由Xbox应用程序继承，允许用户浏览他们的游戏库（包括運行於PC和Xbox平台的游戏），游戏DVR也可以使用键盘快捷方式，允许用户錄下最后30秒的游戏画面，並分享至Xbox Live，[[OneDrive|OneDrive]]或其他地方。 Windows 10还允许用户从本地网络控制和玩Xbox One的游戏。<ref>{{Cite_web|url=https://www.engadget.com/2015/01/21/microsoft-windows-10-xbox/|title=Microsoft makes Xbox features an integral part of Windows 10|accessdate=2017-01-02|work=Engadget|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170102171901/https://www.engadget.com/2015/01/21/microsoft-windows-10-xbox/|archivedate=2017-01-02}}</ref> Xbox Live SDK允许应用程序开发人员将Xbox Live功能集成到他们的应用程序中，未来的无线Xbox One配件（如控制器）在Windows上通过适配器支持。<ref>{{Cite_web|url=http://www.polygon.com/2015/1/21/7867479/xbox-app-windows-10-microsoft-phil-spencer|title=Xbox app coming to Windows 10, Microsoft confirms|accessdate=2017-01-02|date=2015-01-21|last=McWhertor|first=Michael|work=Polygon|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170202141042/http://www.polygon.com/2015/1/21/7867479/xbox-app-windows-10-microsoft-phil-spencer|archivedate=2017-02-02}}</ref>微软也允许Xbox One和Windows 10[[游戏|游戏]]之间的[[同步|同步]]；[[微软工作室|微软工作室]]为Windows 10和Xbox One开發了独家游戏，如《ReCore》和《[[量子破碎|量子破碎]]》。<ref>{{Cite_news|url=http://www.gamespot.com/articles/xbox-one-and-pc-cross-buy-will-be-platform-feature/1100-6434739/?ftag=GSS-05-10aaa0a|title=Xbox One and PC Cross-Buy Will Be "Platform Feature," Says Phil Spencer|newspaper=GameSpot|accessdate=2017-01-02|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170224181743/http://www.gamespot.com/articles/xbox-one-and-pc-cross-buy-will-be-platform-feature/1100-6434739/?ftag=GSS-05-10aaa0a|archivedate=2017-02-24}}</ref>
《[[Candy_Crush_Saga|Candy Crush Saga]]》和《[[Microsoft_Solitaire_Collection|Microsoft Solitaire Collection]]》也会在安装Windows 10时自动一併安装。<ref>{{Cite_news|url=http://www.wired.co.uk/news/archive/2015-07/30/windows-10-paid-ad-removal-solitaire|title=Windows 10 makes you pay to remove ads from Solitaire|last=Kamen|first=Matt|newspaper=WIRED UK|accessdate=2017-01-02|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160508145051/http://www.wired.co.uk/news/archive/2015-07/30/windows-10-paid-ad-removal-solitaire|archivedate=2016-05-08}}</ref><ref>{{Cite_web|url=http://www.polygon.com/2015/1/21/7867545/windows-10-stream-xbox-one-games|title=Windows 10 will let you stream Xbox One games to any Windows 10 PC or tablet (update)|accessdate=2017-01-02|date=2015-01-21|last=Sarkar|first=Samit|work=Polygon|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170202125938/http://www.polygon.com/2015/1/21/7867545/windows-10-stream-xbox-one-games|archivedate=2017-02-02}}</ref>Windows 10引入了全新的「Game bar」，其可對進行记录和截图。用户还可以使操作系统在后台连续记录游戏，然后，用户可以将最后几个自選的游戏时刻保存到硬盘。
Windows 10新增了[[FLAC|FLAC]]和[[HEVC|HEVC]]编解码器，并支持[[Matroska|Matroska]]格式的媒体，允许在Groove音乐和其他应用程序中打开这些格式。<ref>{{Cite_news|url=http://www.pcworld.com/article/2852595/audio-snobs-rejoice-windows-10-will-have-system-wide-flac-support.html|title=Audio snobs rejoice: Windows 10 will have system-wide FLAC support|newspaper=PCWorld|accessdate=2017-01-02|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20161228202246/http://www.pcworld.com/article/2852595/audio-snobs-rejoice-windows-10-will-have-system-wide-flac-support.html|archivedate=2016-12-28}}</ref><ref>{{Cite_web|url=https://www.engadget.com/2014/11/27/windows-10-native-flac-mkv-support/|title=Windows 10 will play your .MKV and .FLAC files all on its own|accessdate=2017-01-02|work=Engadget|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170103002443/https://www.engadget.com/2014/11/27/windows-10-native-flac-mkv-support/|archivedate=2017-01-03}}</ref>
==== DirectX 12 ====
Windows 10內置了[[DirectX|DirectX 12]]及[[Windows_Display_Driver_Model#WDDM2|WDDM 2.0]]<ref name="dx12PreviewAnandtech">{{Cite_web |url=http://anandtech.com/show/8962/the-directx-12-performance-preview-amd-nvidia-star-swarm |title=The DirectX 12 Performance Preview: AMD, NVIDIA, & Star Swarm |date=2015-02-06 |website=Anandtech |publisher=Purch Inc. |access-date=2015-02-06 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150208024115/http://www.anandtech.com/show/8962/the-directx-12-performance-preview-amd-nvidia-star-swarm |archivedate=2015-02-08 }}</ref><ref name="dx12-w10">{{Cite_web |last1=Langley |first1=Bryan |title=DirectX 12 and Windows 10 |url=http://blogs.msdn.com/b/directx/archive/2014/10/01/directx-12-and-windows-10.aspx |website=DirectX Developer Blog |accessdate=2014-10-03 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20141004051236/http://blogs.msdn.com/b/directx/archive/2014/10/01/directx-12-and-windows-10.aspx |archivedate=2014-10-04 }}</ref>。兩者皆於2014年3月的[[游戏开发者大会|游戏开发者大会]]上發布，DirectX 12旨在提供「遊戲機水準的性能」（console-level efficiency）及以更佳的方式進行硬件资源访问，並降低[[CPU|CPU]]和圖形驅動程序的耗用<ref name="pcworld-woogamers">{{Cite_web |title=Windows 10 will woo gamers with supercharged DirectX 12 graphics API |url=http://www.pcworld.com/article/2690788/windows-10-will-woo-gamers-with-supercharged-directx-12-graphics-api.html |website=PCWorld |accessdate=2014-10-03 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20141006031000/http://www.pcworld.com/article/2690788/windows-10-will-woo-gamers-with-supercharged-directx-12-graphics-api.html |archivedate=2014-10-06 }}</ref><ref name="techradar-dx12">{{Cite_web |title=Microsoft details DirectX 12 for better Xbox One, PC performance |url=http://www.techradar.com/news/gaming/microsoft-previews-directx-12-for-better-pc-and-xbox-one-performance-1235804 |website=Techradar |accessdate=2014-10-03 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20141006103703/http://www.techradar.com/news/gaming/microsoft-previews-directx-12-for-better-pc-and-xbox-one-performance-1235804 |archivedate=2014-10-06 }}</ref>。大多數性能改進是靠[[低级语言|低級的编程语言]]來实現，這使得開發人員能更高效地運用資源，並減少因高級API而引起的單線程CPU瓶頸<ref>{{Cite_web |url=http://anandtech.com/show/7889/microsoft-announces-directx-12-low-level-graphics-programming-comes-to-directx/2 |title=Microsoft Announces DirectX 12: Low Level Graphics Programming Comes To DirectX |last1=Smith |first1=Ryan |date=2014-03-24 |website=AnandTech |publisher=Purch Inc. |access-date=2015-03-17 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150404230124/http://www.anandtech.com/show/7889/microsoft-announces-directx-12-low-level-graphics-programming-comes-to-directx/2 |archivedate=2015-04-04 }}</ref><ref>{{Cite_web |url=http://www.anandtech.com/show/9038/next-generation-opengl-becomes-vulkan-additional-details-released |title=Next Generation OpenGL Becomes Vulkan: Additional Details Released |last1=Smith |first1=Ryan |date=2015-03-03 |website=Anandtech |publisher=Purch |access-date=2015-06-20 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150624172154/http://www.anandtech.com/show/9038/next-generation-opengl-becomes-vulkan-additional-details-released |archivedate=2015-06-24 }}</ref>。其還支持多廠商GPU並聯這一種平台設定<ref>{{Cite_web |url=http://www.pcper.com/reviews/Graphics-Cards/BUILD-2015-Final-DirectX-12-Reveal |title=BUILD 2015: The Final DirectX 12 Reveal |last1=Michaud |first1=Scott |date=2015-05-04 |website=PC Perspective |publisher=PC Perspective |access-date=2015-08-22 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150905111424/http://www.pcper.com/reviews/Graphics-Cards/BUILD-2015-Final-DirectX-12-Reveal |archivedate=2015-09-05 }}</ref>。WDDM 2.0則引入了一種全新的虛擬內存管理和分配系統，以減少核心模式驅動程式（kernel-mode driver）的工作負載<ref name="dx12PreviewAnandtech" /><ref>{{Cite_web |url=https://msdn.microsoft.com/en-us/library/windows/hardware/dn932171(v=vs.85).aspx |title=What's new for Windows 10 Insider Preview display drivers (WDDM 2.0) |date= |website=[[MSDN|MSDN]] |publisher=[[Microsoft|Microsoft]] |access-date=2015-06-20 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150701133800/https://msdn.microsoft.com/en-us/library/windows/hardware/dn932171(v=vs.85).aspx |archivedate=2015-07-01 }}</ref>。

=== 裝置与平台统一 ===
{{See Also|Microsoft Lumia 950#作業系統|Windows 10 Mobile}}

Windows 10恢復了原有的[[開始畫面|開始功能表]]，并将[[Windows_8|Windows 8]]系统中的「开始界面」整合其中。現代化應用程式则在桌面以視窗化模式运行。<ref name="autogenerated1">{{Cite_news|title=Windows 10新特性盘点：将适用所有设备|url=http://tech.163.com/14/1001/02/A7EGVFNR00094ODU.html|accessdate=2014-09-30|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20141003090607/http://tech.163.com/14/1001/02/A7EGVFNR00094ODU.html|archivedate=2014-10-03}}</ref>

Windows 10为所有硬體提供一个统一的平台以及支持广泛的设备类型，从物联网设备到全球企业数据中心服务器。其中一些设备屏幕只有4英寸，一些设备的屏幕则有80英寸，有些甚至没有屏幕。有些设备是手持类型，有的则需要远程操控。这些设备的操作方法各不相同，手触控、笔触控、鼠标键盘，以及动作控制器，微软都将全部支持。这些设备将会拥有类似的功能，微软的[[UWP|UWP]]正为此设计。<ref name="pcworld-universalapps">{{Cite_web|title=Microsoft's universal Windows apps run on tablets, phones, Xbox, and PCs|url=http://www.pcworld.com/article/2138625/microsoft-introduces-universal-apps-that-scale-across-phones-tablets-and-pcs.html|work=PC World|publisher=IDG|accessdate=2014-09-30|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140405014946/http://www.pcworld.com/article/2138625/microsoft-introduces-universal-apps-that-scale-across-phones-tablets-and-pcs.html|archivedate=2014-04-05}}</ref><ref name="feature"/>

Windows 10覆盖所有尺寸和品类的Windows设备，所有设备将共享一个应用商店。因为启用了Windows Runtime，用户可以跨平台地在Windows设备（[[手机|手机]]、[[平板电脑|平板电脑]]、[[个人电脑|个人电脑]]以及[[Xbox|Xbox]]等）上运行同一个应用。<ref name="pcworld-universalapps"/><ref name="feature"/>

Windows 10 Mobile是Windows 10作業系統的分支版本。此版本是专为屏幕尺寸低于8寸的[[智能手机|智能手机]]和平板电脑而設。運行Windows Phone 8.1的智能手机可升级至Windows 10 Mobile，<ref name="ArsTechnica">{{Cite_news|last=Bright|first=Peter|title=所有Windows Phone8手机将获得Windows 10，除了部分手机不会|url=http://arstechnica.com/gadgets/2015/01/every-windows-phone-8-phone-will-get-windows-10-except-the-ones-that-wont/|newspaper=Ars Technica|date=2015-01-24|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150208230925/http://arstechnica.com/gadgets/2015/01/every-windows-phone-8-phone-will-get-windows-10-except-the-ones-that-wont/|archivedate=2015-02-08|accessdate=2015-08-13}}</ref>但一些功能取决于硬體設備的兼容性。<ref>{{Cite_web |url=https://www.thurrott.com/windows/windows-10/1195/yes-windows-10-coming-low-end-windows-phones |title=Yes, Windows 10 is Coming to Low-End Windows Phones |date=2015-02-09 |website=thurrot.com |publisher=Petri |access-date=2015-02-11 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150211085348/https://www.thurrott.com/windows/windows-10/1195/yes-windows-10-coming-low-end-windows-phones |archivedate=2015-02-11 }}</ref><ref>{{Cite_news|last1=Devine|first1=Richard|title=Windows10技术预览版手机版本现在可以下载！|url=http://www.windowscentral.com/windows-10-technical-preview-phones-now-available-download|accessdate=2015-02-12|work=Windows Central|agency=Mobile Nations|date=2015-02-12|ref=Win10Misout|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150212231255/http://www.windowscentral.com/windows-10-technical-preview-phones-now-available-download|archivedate=2015-02-12}}</ref>

Windows 10重視不同设备之间的同步，尤其是在设备运行Windows版本的[[Wintel|电脑]]和智慧型手机。Windows 10電腦的[[Windows_Runtime|Windows Runtime]]应用程式可以[[移植_(軟體)|移植]]到Windows 10 Mobile，并分享共同的代码库。Windows 10 Mobile與个人电脑版本分享同樣的用户界面元素，但与桌面版本不同的是，不会有多用户登录功能。<ref name=verge-universalpreview>{{Cite_web|title=微软Windows10预览版通用应用横跨个人电脑、平板电脑和手机|url=http://www.theverge.com/2015/1/21/7866941/windows-previews-universal-apps-for-windows-10-pcs-tablets-and-phones|website=The Verge|accessdate=2015-02-07|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150204080608/http://www.theverge.com/2015/1/21/7866941/windows-previews-universal-apps-for-windows-10-pcs-tablets-and-phones|archivedate=2015-02-04}}</ref><ref name="auto"/>

== 移除的功能 ==
Windows 10不会包含[[Windows_Media_Center|Windows Media Center]]，并在[[升级|升级]]Windows 10时卸载。由于所需的[[DVD|DVD]][[解码器|解码器]]的许可成本以及没有光驱的PC设备数量的增加，Microsoft先前已将Media Center和集成的[[DVD|DVD]]播放支持降级到付费插件。<ref>{{Cite_news|url=http://gadgets.ndtv.com/laptops/news/microsoft-lists-features-youll-lose-when-upgrading-to-windows-10-698973|title=Microsoft Lists Features You'll Lose When Upgrading to Windows 10|newspaper=NDTV Gadgets360.com|accessdate=2016-12-30|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170202211245/http://gadgets.ndtv.com/laptops/news/microsoft-lists-features-youll-lose-when-upgrading-to-windows-10-698973|archivedate=2017-02-02}}</ref>

[[OneDrive|OneDrive]]内置同步客户端（在Windows 8.1中引入）不再支持Windows 10中的纯在线文件的离线占位符。查看离线文件的功能预计将来会被新的Windows应用程序替代。<ref>{{Cite_web|url=http://www.theverge.com/2015/7/30/9076445/mozilla-microsoft-windows-10-browser-default-apps-complaint|title=Mozilla blasts Microsoft for making it harder to switch to Firefox in Windows 10|accessdate=2016-12-30|date=2015-07-30|last=Warren|first=Tom|work=The Verge|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170127082326/http://www.theverge.com/2015/7/30/9076445/mozilla-microsoft-windows-10-browser-default-apps-complaint|archivedate=2017-01-27}}</ref>

用户无法再在与Microsoft帐户关联的所有设备上同步开始菜单布局。 Microsoft开发人员解释用户可能有不同的应用程序，他们想强调他们在使用的是不同设备，而不是在使用相同的配置。在与帐户关联的所有设备上自动安装[[Windows商店|Windows 应用商店]]应用的能力也被删除。<ref name="asdf">{{Cite_news|url=https://www.thurrott.com/cloud/microsoft-consumer-services/bing/4571/microsoft-is-shutting-down-some-msn-mobile-apps|title=Microsoft is Shutting Down Some MSN Mobile Apps|date=2015-07-10|newspaper=Thurrott.com|accessdate=2016-12-30|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20161127203716/https://www.thurrott.com/cloud/microsoft-consumer-services/bing/4571/microsoft-is-shutting-down-some-msn-mobile-apps|archivedate=2016-11-27}}</ref>

浏览器不能再在没有用户操作的情况下将自己设置为默认；更改默认[[浏览器|浏览器]]必须由用户从“设置”的“默认应用”页面手动设置。<ref name='asdf' />

